Sketching a small WebGL scene graph library

Goals:
  - Put together quick presentation graphics
  - Make simple things simple
    - Loading and displaying simple textured models
      - Load archives with model and textures using XMLHttpRequest
    - Drawing text
      - Draw text using the 2D canvas
      - Billboard text
    - Applying post-processing filters
      - Perspective and ortho cameras with possible FBO render targets
      - Material system 
    - Animation
      - Animation vocabulary
      - Transformation tweens
      - Follow along Bezier curves & Catmull-Rom splines
    - User inputs
      - Default camera navigation
      - Event handlers
